  <brief_title>PET Respiratory Gating to Detect Hepatic Metastasis in Patients With Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Respiratory Gating on FDG/PET Detection of Hepatic Metastasis in Patients With Colon Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
